OL,3,CDid the King just deliver the verbal
OL,4,Cequivalent of burning down the White
OL,5,CHouse?
OL,7,FKing Charles quoted "my Prime
OL,8,FMinister" and reminded Congress that
OL,9,Fthe UK recognises the threat.
OL,11,F"That is why our country, in order to
OL,12,Fbe fit for the future, has committed
OL,13,Fto the biggest sustained increase in
OL,14,Fdefence spending since the Cold War",
OL,15,Fhe said referring the British
OL,16,Fgovernment's commitment.
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@IO]vD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
