OL,3,CDid the King just deliver the verbal
OL,4,Cequivalent of burning down the White
OL,5,CHouse?
OL,7,FHe spoke of his own service in the
OL,8,FRoyal Navy, the aircraft carriers of
OL,9,Fwhich Donald Trump recently called
OL,10,F"toys" and Secretary of War, Pete
OL,11,FHegseth has similarly disparaged.
OL,13,FAhead of his visit to the 9/11
OL,14,Fmemorial in New York, the King spoke
OL,15,Fabout the only time the NATO Alliance
OL,16,Fhas invoked Article 5 (an attack on
OL,17,Fone country is considered an attack on
OL,18,Fall members).
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
