OL,3,CDid the King just deliver the verbal
OL,4,Cequivalent of burning down the White
OL,5,CHouse?
OL,7,FAt that time, came the words, "we
OL,8,Fanswered the call together ` as our
OL,9,Fpeople have done so for more than a
OL,10,Fcentury, shoulder to shoulder, through
OL,11,Ftwo World Wars, the Cold War,
OL,12,FAfghanistan and moments that have
OL,13,Fdefined our shared security."
OL,15,FA succinct way of responding to the
OL,16,Ferroneous claim by Donald Trump that
OL,17,FNATO (and British) troops were "a
OL,18,Flittle back, a little off" the
OL,19,Ffrontline.
OL,26,@uD@]O]yD@`OU
