OL,3,CDid the King just deliver the verbal
OL,4,Cequivalent of burning down the White
OL,5,CHouse?
OL,7,FThat led into a call for support for
OL,8,FUkraine following the full-scale
OL,9,FRussian invasion, which is now into
OL,10,Fits fifth year.
OL,12,F"Today, Mr. Speaker, that same,
OL,13,Funyielding resolve is needed for the
OL,14,Fdefence of Ukraine and her most
OL,15,Fcourageous people ` in order to secure
OL,16,Fa truly just and lasting peace."
OL,26,@xD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
